query:
/*+  */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.favorite_count >= 0 AND q1.favorite_count <= 10000
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('14.04',
'bash',
'boot',
'command-line',
'drivers',
'gnome',
'nvidia',
'partitioning',
'scripts',
'server',
'shortcut-keys',
'sound',
'system-installation',
'upgrade')
inner join answer AS a1
on a1.question_id = q1.id
inner join so_user AS u1
on a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.reputation >= 0 AND u1.reputation <= 100
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('askubuntu') group by t1.name;
